        <refsect1>

            <title>Description</title>

            <para>
                Oftentimes, it is impractical to reimplement large software projects using more appropriate programming languages. It is the goal of
                <productname>the Modern C Library</productname> to provide C programmers with support for modern practices in such situations.
            </para>

        </refsect1>

